    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs pass the pre-registered E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given that the COU is scoped exclusively to ASTM F1717 compression-bending and the experimental evidence base (N=11, two laboratories) is sufficient for medium model influence and medium decision consequence. Experimental evidence supports the validation results; the claim of FEA accuracy is considered credible for the stated COU.",
